"
" Vim-friendly keybindings for Colemak.
"
" Remaps as few commands as possible with a goal of keeping the most
" important keys (the movement keys) in the same physical place.

" Searching
nnoremap k n
vnoremap k n

" Movement
nnoremap n gj
nnoremap e gk
nnoremap i l

vnoremap n gj
vnoremap e gk
vnoremap i l

vnoremap s i
vnoremap S I
nnoremap s i
nnoremap S I
omap s i

